## Install

```bash
pnpm install
```

First-time Claude Code marketplace registration on a new machine:

```text
/plugin marketplace add patinaproject/skills
```

The plugins this repo depends on are declared in `.claude/settings.json` under `enabledPlugins` and will be picked up automatically once the marketplace is registered.

## Development

- `pnpm lint:md` — lint all Markdown.
- Commits must follow `type: #<issue> short description` (enforced by husky).
- PR titles follow the same format.

